<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>EECS Girls Who Tech Camp — CTF Challenge</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="EECS Girls Who Tech Camp" class="logo">
      <h1>Capture The Flag Challenge</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Become a cybersecurity hero — 6 fun challenges await!</p>
      <div class="scoreboard">
        <span class="score-label">Solved</span>
        <span class="score-number" id="score"><%= solved.length %></span>
        <span class="score-total">/ 6</span>
        <div class="progress-bar">
          <div class="progress-fill" style="width: <%= (solved.length / 6 * 100) %>%"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <br>
      <a href="/reset" class="reset-btn">Reset Progress</a>
    </header>

    <div class="challenges-grid">

      <div class="challenge-card <%= solved.includes('ch1') ? 'solved' : '' %>">
        <div class="card-badge">Web</div>
        <div class="card-difficulty">⭐</div>
        <h3>👀 The Hidden Secret</h3>
        <p>Mei built a personal webpage and hid a secret inside. But you can't see anything on the page... can you find it?</p>
        <p class="hint-text">Hint: There's more to a webpage than meets the eye</p>
        <a href="/challenge/1" class="play-btn">Start Challenge →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="challenge-card <%= solved.includes('ch2') ? 'solved' : '' %>">
        <div class="card-badge">Web</div>
        <div class="card-difficulty">⭐</div>
        <h3>🍪 Cookie Monster</h3>
        <p>Someone hid a secret inside your browser's "cookies." Do you know how to peek inside them?</p>
        <p class="hint-text">Hint: F12 is your best friend</p>
        <a href="/challenge/2" class="play-btn">Start Challenge →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="challenge-card <%= solved.includes('ch3') ? 'solved' : '' %>">
        <div class="card-badge">Web</div>
        <div class="card-difficulty">⭐⭐</div>
        <h3>🤖 The Robot's Secret</h3>
        <p>Every website has a special file that tells search engines which pages to stay away from... but you're not a robot, right?</p>
        <p class="hint-text">Hint: The filename is related to "robots"</p>
        <a href="/challenge/3" class="play-btn">Start Challenge →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="challenge-card <%= solved.includes('ch4') ? 'solved' : '' %>">
        <div class="card-badge forensics">Forensics</div>
        <div class="card-difficulty">⭐⭐</div>
        <h3>📸 Secrets in a Photo</h3>
        <p>A seemingly ordinary photo — but digital detectives know that every photo "talks." Can you find its hidden message?</p>
        <p class="hint-text">Hint: Photos carry invisible information beyond the picture</p>
        <a href="/challenge/4" class="play-btn">Start Challenge →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="challenge-card <%= solved.includes('ch5') ? 'solved' : '' %>">
        <div class="card-badge forensics">Forensics</div>
        <div class="card-difficulty">⭐⭐</div>
        <h3>📋 Log Detective</h3>
        <p>A server was attacked! Analyze the access logs and find the flag the hacker left behind in a suspicious request.</p>
        <p class="hint-text">Hint: Read every line carefully — some requests look fishy...</p>
        <a href="/challenge/5" class="play-btn">Start Challenge →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="challenge-card <%= solved.includes('ch6') ? 'solved' : '' %>">
        <div class="card-badge forensics">Forensics</div>
        <div class="card-difficulty">⭐⭐⭐</div>
        <h3>🔮 The Mystery File</h3>
        <p>You received a mysterious file with a <code>.dat</code> extension — but it's actually another file type in disguise! Can you uncover its true identity?</p>
        <p class="hint-text">Hint: The first few bytes of a file reveal its true nature</p>
        <a href="/challenge/6" class="play-btn">Start Challenge →</a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <footer>
      <p>Every answer follows the format: <code>flag{...}</code></p>
      <p>Stuck? Try searching the web for the concepts mentioned in each challenge!</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 12px; opacity: 0.5;">EECS Girls Who Tech Camp</p>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script>
    const solved = <%= solved.length %>;
    if (solved === 6) {
      document.querySelector('.subtitle').textContent = '🎊 All challenges complete — you are a true cybersecurity hero! 🎊';
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
